# Books API

도서 정보를 제공하는 API 입니다.

## Books Collection [/books]

### List All Books [GET /books/{?title,offset,limit}]

+ Parameters
    + title (optional) - a book title variable
    + offset (optional) - start offset
    + limit (optional) - total count of books
    
+ Response 200 (application/json)

